data.description: Conveniently located just 1.8 miles to Panama City Beach, this condo offers a bright, open interior, as well as a covered balcony overlooking the community courtyard. You'll enjoy hardwood flooring throughout the open-concept living and dining area, making for a great place to entertain family and friends. The kitchen offers adequate cabinet storage, countertop space, and a flat-top range. Granite countertops shine, and the kitchen island with breakfast-bar seating ties all three spaces together. The spacious living room and dining area show off abundant natural light with twin french doors leading to the balcony.
